column2: Wow, we had so many messages from our fans yesterday, thank you so much for your input, but more importantly thanks for your support! We love what we do, and we especially love our fans! We will continue to work hard to get on the podium this season! Here is another excellent photo from the Mexico ePrix, courtesy of @kalatas.#GEOXDRAGON#ABBFormulaE#MexicoCityEPrix

Check out our Stories and send us a DM with how you think we are doing, and we will send you a very special present  AMAZING photo taken by @ricardobanuelosm / @automovmex! Thanks for sharing Ricardo.#GEOXDRAGON#ABBFormulaE#MexicoCityEPrix

Click the link in our Bio to read some insights by @felipenasr about his first ABB FIA Formula E race of his Career last weekend in Mexico City. #GEOXDRAGON#ABBFormulaE#MexicoCityEPrix#NoRiskNoReward#ArgoLife

Final in-season Test for this year. Thank you Mxico City, you have been a fantastic host for us this last week. Bring on Hong Kong!Final de la temporada de prueba por este ao. Muchas gracias Ciudad de Mxico, ustedes fueron un fantstico anfitrin esta semana. Hong Kong all vamos!#GEOXDRAGON#ABBFormulaE#MexicoCityEPrix

After a disappointing race in Mexico City, we have testing tomorrow, and head to Asia for round 5 in Hong Kong in a few weeks. Keep the boys motivated with your comments below!Despus de una decepcionante carrera en Ciudad de Mxico, maana continuaremos con pruebas para la siguiente carrera en Hong Kong dentro de pocas semanas. Mantengamos a los muchachos motivados con sus comentarios!Depois duma corrida decepcionante na Cidade do Mxico, temos testes amanh pra a prxima rodada no Hong Kong em poucas semanas. Mantenhamos os meninos motivados com seus comentrios abaixo.#GEOXDRAGON#ABBFormulaE#MexicoCityEPrix

DRAGON is pleased to announce a multiyear strategic alliance with GEOX. The Italian footwear and outerwear company will become title partner of our Racing Team beginning in Season 5 of the ABB FIA Formula E Championship. Our team will be re-named GEOX DRAGON to reflect the deep strategic integration of both organizations.Make sure you tag our new name on all Major Social Platforms, @GEOXDRAGON!#GEOXDRAGON#ABBFormulaE#GEOXPERIENCE

Yesterday, California Governor Jerry Brown signed legislation that would require all of the States electricity to come from Carbon-Free sources by 2045, marking the biggest step yet in Californias fight against Global Warming.@DragonRacing is very proud to have our home in California, and to be part of the #SustainableLiving movement.Read the article via the link in our Bio to find out more.Ayer, el Gobernador de California, Jerry Brown, firm una legislacin que requerira que toda la electricidad del estado provenga de fuentes libres de carbono para el ao 2045, lo que representa el mayor paso en la lucha de California contra el calentamiento global.@DragonRacing est muy orgulloso de tener nuestro hogar en California y de ser parte del movimiento #SustainableLiving.Lea el artculo a travs del enlace en nuestra biografa para obtener ms informacin.#DragonRacing#ABBFormulaE#EPluribusUnum
